      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im taking sertraline for my mood but things have been pretty rough lately with finals coming up. i was looking at st johns wort at the drugstore and was wondering if it would be okay to take that too to help boost my mood? i feel like since its just a herbal supplement it should be fine to mix with my meds right?",
